Subject:[CT Birds] Black scoters in Canton
Raft of 20 black scoters on Nepaug Reservoir, Canton.  (with Jay Kaplan and Jamie Meyers)

Also Ring-necked ducks, hooded mergansers, one wood duck, and mallards at Mills Pond, Canton

Sarah Faulkner
Collinsville


